Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THUNDER GATE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:04.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FIVE YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SEPTEMBER 12, 2034\NTEN YEARS SINCE THE CALAMITY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five years ago,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we made our living{\i}\N{\i1}in the Electro-Kart Racing industry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TEAM FUNAYAMA - KIRIKO TAKEHAYA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Katayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,-Come back!\N-Stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Takehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't chase them too far! Haruki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But that little brat has seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been looking after\Nour young lad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin!\NThese guys have been making fake tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,TENGOKU-DAIMAKYO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,TENGOKU-DAIMAKYO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could kill me\Nwith a tiny scrap of metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Haruki, when you fight your enemies,\Nyou don't need to stare into their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Glaring is just something cowards do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,when they want to get away\Nwith only intimidating their opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Avoid the eyes,\Nand concentrate on the collar instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Then focus on the ground,\Ncheck how it feels beneath your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who do nothing\Nbut look at their opponents, lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's hand these guys over to the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Haruki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want something, just ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What meat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Monkey, crow and mouse. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a little baggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,He'll grow into it quickly, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I want something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,How about trousers?\NBet they'll fit if you cut them in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,My legs are not that short!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see? I was disqualified.\NI fell out of my kart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Did you hurt yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm okay.\NThe other drivers went around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so dangerous.\NYou gotta be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You really should drive more safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,REPORTS OF SPECTATORS\NGOING MISSING
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I attached a flash to my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take some new photos to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Take one of me and Doc, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,-Time to go.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Haruki, I heard the doc\Nis researching "Man-eaters,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and even experimenting on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin's investigating at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,But it'd be better if Kiriko\Ndidn't get too close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}CURRENTLY IN USE\NBY FUNAYAMA ORPHANAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,KIRIKO AND HARUKI TAKEHAYA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Haruki, aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanna get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're actually getting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a Man-eater in the third district!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not coming this way,\Nso go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,-Let's go, Robin!\N-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I have the gun that I made,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,and I want to be helpful to Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I think about those days…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they seem like heaven to me now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,KIRIKO AND HARUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You killed a Man-eater\Nwith that weapon last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:33.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing around!\NI told you not to come. It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I made Robin angry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, Robin had a sister my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,He lost her in the Great Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Since then, he's been overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Which watch is right again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,-That one.\N-Twenty after two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to go! Sis's race starts at three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin might be overprotective,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,but that guy is obsessed with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SEPTEMBER 20, 2034\NTEN YEARS SINCE THE CALAMITY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, just made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a Man-eater\Nat the end of the track!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It can turn invisible,\Nsame as the one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All karts are off at once!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of race will it be today?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Man-eater's gone into the arcade.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's probably seven or eight minutes{\i}\N{\i1}until the karts get there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll drive it away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I can do it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the long straight,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}karts eight, three and four{\i}\N{\i1}round the second corner.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:34.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a crash for two and five,{\i}\N{\i1}a spin that will set them way back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The rest are off towards Sensoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number four, Takehaya,{\i}\N{\i1}you pulled that off well!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,-Goddamn it!\N-Nice one, Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has it left the course?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable, it barely hurt it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally, got a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,My arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's eating me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takehaya's in the lead,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}exiting the third corner{\i}\N{\i1}towards the arcade.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll be momentarily out of sight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Asakusa Race Association{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is in the process of arranging for cameras{\i}\N{\i1}to be installed throughout the course.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you can offer such a service,{\i}\N{\i1}then by all means, please get in touch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop! There's a Man-eater!\NCall the race off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back and tell the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Haruki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Haruki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Give him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Haru… No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Anybody, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so close.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}CURRENTLY IN USE\NBY FUNAYAMA ORPHANAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My head…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so hot.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Takehaya has regained consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently,\Nthere's another Man-eater in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and a child is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Si-- Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,The patient, she--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Takehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be walking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm Haruki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,-Where's Sis?\N-Get a tranquilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,-Going!\N-I want my sister! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,-You need to calm down.\N-Sis! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I think that\Nthe shock of her brother's death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,has led her to believe\Nthat she is her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What did the doctor do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.19,Main,,0,0,0,,He must know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,After giving you both medical attention,\Nthe doctor left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You were both brought here\Non the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,SURGERY IN PROGRESS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to your brother\Nis incredibly upsetting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but no matter what treatment we used,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,without the doctor,\NI believe you would both be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,--SOJI HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last time I saw her,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she was crying, but definitely alive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was she eaten by the Man-eater?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One thing is undeniable.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am definitely still Haruki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The proof of that{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the sorrow splintering through me{\i}\N{\i1}at the news of my sister's death,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the occasional faint solace{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of having inherited{\i}\N{\i1}the body of someone I love.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the time my sister's wounds had healed,{\i}\N{\i1}and I could start to move her body again,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nearly four months had passed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Robin must be investigating{\i}\N{\i1}what that doctor was up to.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure he will be able to figure it out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll be able to tell me{\i}\N{\i1}why I have become my sister,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and why she had to die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,ASAKUSA RACE ASSOCIATION\NHEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping to see Robin Inazaki\Nfrom the Asakusa Race Association--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sometime around September last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was an increase in disappearances{\i}\N{\i1}around here last year.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems he got tangled up{\i}\N{\i1}in trying to investigate.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, just like that,{\i}\N{\i1}he ended up disappearing too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ken! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! What happened to\Nthe orphanage that was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,-It was moved elsewhere.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Their highest earning racer died…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,REPORTS OF SPECTATORS\NGOING MISSING
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,…and the leader went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I expect with all the bad luck,\Nthey gave up on this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, just like that,{\i}\N{\i1}he ended up disappearing too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The leader went missing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Missing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Disappeared"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,There isn't actually any proof\Nthat Robin is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.51,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way Robin can be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,He must be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor has the answer to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Where Robin is, why my sister is dead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,and why I'm living inside her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,TRIP GUARD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,PROTECTION FROM WILD ANIMALS,\NBANDITS AND MAN-EATERS - KIRUKO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, I lived in various towns,{\i}\N{\i1}searching for the two of them,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}accepting requests,{\i}\N{\i1}and doing everything by myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Four years later, I met you in Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,DO NOT ENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've told anyone that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to check something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Would it be better\Nif I stopped calling you "Sis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been calling me that for a month,\Npretty sure we're both used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, there you go.\NYou'll have to think of me as a man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wrap my mind around it\Njust like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\Nyou're getting pretty good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll meet someone\Nmore appropriate soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't find a girl\NI get along with this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because we're both guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So the photo of Jane Inamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Robin Inazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,we grew up in the same house,\Nso I guess he's like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But he's also a close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose I admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Because we're both guys! I look up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you expect\Nwhen you tell someone something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe a good night's sleep\Nwill sort your head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe when I wake up\Nthis will all turn out to be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What now? What's the racket for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,There was a huge fish outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The window is wet,\Neven though it's not raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Maru, go and tell the captain\Nto keep an eye--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,A Man-eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I promised to give this one to Tokio.\NYou can have the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:05.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I like your weird drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You think it's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously! Proper babies--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Climbing on tables is forbidden, Kuku.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop annoying Kona and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be nasty about them,\Nthen stop asking for Kona's drawings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I was saying they were good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've seen one. A real baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Real babies don't have faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Want to go and see it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（人々のざわめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.97,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）５年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:17.39,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕らは電動カートレースの\N興行を生業にしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客１）頼むぞ 尾崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（エンジン音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:23.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客２）片山！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客３）桐子きりこちゃーん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:29.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客たちの歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希はるきの息切れ）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）待て！\N（ケン）待て オラッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（詐欺師）ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:39.16,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レーサー１）ハッ！ 竹早たけはやか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:47.88,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）ハアハア… ハア… ハア\N（ケン）深追いするな　春希！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:51.88,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レーサー２）ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:53.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ふっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:57.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:57.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ぐわっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.81,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（詐欺師１･２）\Nハア… ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,早く 逃げようぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:05.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いや コイツには顔を見られた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ…　うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.44,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（近づく足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ロビン）ウチの若いもんが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,随分 世話になってる\Nみたいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:25.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビン！ コイツらニセの車券を\N作ってやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（詐欺師２）ううっ… うう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:31.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うあああーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:36.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:00.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,う… うう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:08.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ロビン）そんな金属片で\N俺を殺せると思ったのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:15.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希 ケンカする時は\N相手から目をそらしてもいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,相手の目をにらむなんてのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:21.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,威嚇だけで事なきを得ようって\Nチキンがやることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,目をそらして相手の襟を見な
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:30.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それから地面 足の裏で\N立っている感触を確かめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:30.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ケンカは相手しか\N見えなくなってるヤツが負ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,コイツらは上のもんに引き渡す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希 お前の手柄だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.68,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なんか欲しいもんがあったら言え
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）ただいま！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それ なんの肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（蘭らん）猿と… カラスとネズミかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あれ そのジャンパー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンにもらった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハハッ ちょっとでかいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,すぐ ちょうどよくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:10.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,へ～ いいな～ 私もなんか欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.08,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,じゃ ズボンでももらえば\N半分に切れば履けるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なっ！ そんなに足短くないわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（一同の笑い）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）おなかすいた～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ケン）ん？\N（春希）姉ちゃん おかえり！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ケン）ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）何着だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,見てなかったの？ 落車して棄権
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（３人）えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ケガは？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,後続の人がよけてくれたから平気
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ね 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）\N危ない！ マジで気をつけろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（医者）本当に気をつけた方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,分かった 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ そうだ 桐子ちゃん　へっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,私のカメラに\Nフラッシュ付いたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,新しいブロマイド\N作って売ろうよ フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.41,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 先生と１枚撮ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕はいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,撮るよー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.50,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（蘭）えへへ\N（医者）もう行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うん ありがとう 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希 あの医者\N隠れて人食いの研究したり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,人体実験してるって話だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ええっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ケン）今 ロビンが調べてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:17.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あんまり桐子ちゃんを\N近づけないほうがいいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）春希 寒くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）うん 姉ちゃんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.50,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,寒い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）\Nえっ？ じゃあこっち入る？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ ほ… 本当に入るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（複数の足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子･春希）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,３丁目に人食いが出た！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こっちには来させねーから\N気にせず寝てろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（男１）行くぞ ロビン！\N（ロビン）はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）んっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,大丈夫！ 僕の作った銃もあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンの役に立ちたいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:14.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\N思えばこの頃が 僕にとっての
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,“天国〟だったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（発射音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（お兄）すげえじゃん\N（春希）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:27.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,先週 その武器で\N人食い退治したんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,遊びでやってんじゃねえ\N危ねえから来んなつっただろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,…って怒られたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンは10年前の大災害で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:44.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（子供たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕と同じ歳の妹を亡くしてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:48.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,だから… 何て言うかちょっと\N過保護なんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！ あっと 今 何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:56.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（妹）えーっと\N合ってる時計はどれかいなあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:06:59.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,おっ ２時20分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）いかん！\N３時から姉ちゃんのレースだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,またねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（お兄）\Nロビンは過保護かもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,アイツはシスコンだね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そだねー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.39,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客たちの歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（エンジン音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）よし 間に合った…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（シャッターを踏む音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（シャッターを踏む音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ 誰か！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.39,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,コースの終盤に 人食いがいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:56.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客たちの歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この前と同じ 透明になるやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（観客１）桐ちゃーん！\N（観客２）がんばれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（エンジン音･歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（実況）さあ 各車一斉に\Nスタートしていきました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,今日は一体 どんなレースが\N待っているのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん…　くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）\N人食いが入っていったアーケードに\Nハア ハア ハア ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,カートが来るまで\N７～８分はあるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕が追い払う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕がやるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（実況）長い直線を終え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,第２コーナーを曲がったのは\N８番 ３番 ４番 うわーっと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,５番 ２番がここでスピン！\N大きく遅れた！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,集団はそのまま浅草寺へ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,４番 竹早 上手く引き剥がした！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,桐子ちゃん いいぞお！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,コースから出たのか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.11,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そこか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ビックリするほど効いてない…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:12.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（片山）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:20.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）フウ… フウ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フウ… フウ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（深呼吸）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（人食いのうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）やった 手応えが… うわあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ！ うわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,手が！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（うめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,放せっ… うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（おびえる声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,食われる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,助けて ロビン！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（実況）先頭４番 竹早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,第３コーナーを抜けてアーケードへ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,さて ここからしばらく\N放送席からも追えなくなります
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:08.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ただいま 浅草レース会では\N全コースに中継カメラの…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レーサー）ん？ なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）止まれ！ 人食いが出た\Nレースは無効だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,戻って本部に知らせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レーサー）おっ おう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（奇妙な音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（奇妙な音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（奇妙な音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:49.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（人食いのうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.86,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子）ううっ… う…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:53.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,かえ… せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,春希を… 返せーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:06.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,う… うそ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:13.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,やだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（むせび泣く声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.39,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ひい… 誰か… 誰か早く…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,誰かーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）姉… ちゃん… だ\N（桐子の泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:35.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桐子の泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,近い… なあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ね… ちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（発砲音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）みんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,熱い…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉… ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（発砲音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.48,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ 姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:47.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ハッ！ ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女性）ハア… ハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ…\N竹早さんの意識が戻りました！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（患者１）また人食いが出たってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,子供が１人 亡くなったと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（患者２）ムゴいなあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あの… ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.44,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ… えっ え…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（患者１･２）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）あれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ… ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ね…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん？ わあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ… わあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.08,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女性）３０１の…\N（男性）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ…！ ああ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.17,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ… ああ… ああ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女性）竹早さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.17,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,歩くのは まだ無理よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うるさい！ 僕は春希だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）姉ちゃんどこ！\N姉ちゃんに会いたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（男性１）鎮静剤！\N（男性２）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:55.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うう… 姉ちゃん… 姉ちゃーん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（男性１）\N落ち着いて ああ… ね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女性）恐らく\N弟を死なせてしまったショックから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）う… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,自分を弟だと\N思い込んでいるようです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（男性１）かわいそうに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）医者は…？\N（男性１）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）あの医者が何かしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,アイツなら分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,医者はどこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:24.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,先生はあなたたちの治療をした後\Nこの町を去りました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:25.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:30.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女性）あなたたち姉弟は\N２人とも瀕死の状態で担ぎ込まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:37.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,弟さんのことは残念だったけど\Nどういう治療をしたにせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,先生がいなければ\N２人とも死んでいたと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）分からない…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,最後に見た姉ちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,泣いてたけど ちゃんと生きてた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:59.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あの後 姉ちゃんも\N人食いにやられちゃったのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:05.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,確かなことは\N自分が春希だということ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:12.01,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,その証拠に 確実に襲ってくる\N姉を失った悲しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そして 時折もたげる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:21.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,好きな女の体を手に入れた\N薄暗い喜び
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:27.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんの体のケガが癒え\Nある程度動けるようになった頃には
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,入院から４ヵ月近く経っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:38.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンは医者の裏の顔を\N探ってたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンならきっと調べられる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,どうして僕が\N姉ちゃんになっているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なんで姉ちゃんが死んじゃったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レース会の男）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:53.55,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,浅草レース会の稲崎いなざき露敏ろびんに\N会いたいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ そりゃ無理だなあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.81,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンは去年の９月頃だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,たぶん 殺されちまってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:04.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハアハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レース会の男）\N去年この辺で失踪事件が増えて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それ絡みで犯人を\N調査してたらしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,結局 本人もそのまま消えちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハアハア… うっ… ハア
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ケン！ 蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:23.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,園長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,みんなっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,すみません！\Nこ… ここにあった船山ふなやま孤児院は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（通行人）どこか よそへ行ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:38.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,え…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（通行人）稼ぎ頭だったレーサーが\N事故で亡くなったり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,リーダー格の子が行方不明とかで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:50.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,は… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いろいろ不幸が重なって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この町でやっていけく\Nなったんだろうねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ドアが閉まる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ベットに倒れ込む音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビン… うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（レース会の男）\N結局 本人もそのまま消えちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:24.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（通行人）\Nリーダー格の子が行方不明とかで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,行方不明？ 消えちまった？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.44,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,まだロビンが死んだっていう\N確証がないじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンが死ぬわけない…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,絶対どこかで生きてる！ ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:44.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,医者だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,医者が全部知ってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:51.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ロビンの行方も\N姉ちゃんが死んだ理由も…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うう… うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕が姉ちゃんになって\N生きてる理由も！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）それから\N２人を探して いろんな街に住み
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,依頼をこなし １人で何でも\Nできるようになって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:14.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それから４年ほどして\N中野で君と出会ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.41,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こんな話を人にしたのは初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）１つ確認したいんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん… って\N呼ばないほうがよかったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いや いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:39.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,もう１ヵ月近く呼ばれてるし\Nお互い慣れてるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:44.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ま そういうワケなので\N僕のことは男だと思っておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そんな急にムリだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.68,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ん… ん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,君 ちょっといないくらい\N美少年だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,すぐふさわしい相手見つかるって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.48,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こんな気が合う女の人\N見つかんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それは頭が男同士だから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:06.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\N写真の… 稲村ジェーンだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,稲崎ロビンね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\Nその人のことはどう思ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そうだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ずっと同じ家で育ったから\N家族みたいなもんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,親友でもあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.01,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,憧れてもいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ん～…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,だから！ 同性としてだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,君 まだ混乱してるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こんなフラれ方したら\Nそりゃ混乱もするよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,１回寝て 頭を整理しなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）そうする\N起きたらこの話も夢になってるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（船客１）うわあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,何よっ うるさいな！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:45.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,わ… わあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.16,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）どうした！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,窓の外にでっかい魚がいたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,確かに 雨も降っていないのに\N窓の外が濡れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:58.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,妙だな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,マル 一応警戒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,船長に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.55,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル･船客１）わっ わっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,人食いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:40.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.86,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）ん… ん…っと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:52.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ンフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）これ 赤ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この絵 僕にちょうだいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:01.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（コナ）これは トキオにあげる\N約束だから この次ね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:05.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,やった！ コナの絵はヘンでいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:05.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:06.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（コナ）フッ… ヘンかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:10.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ヘンだよ\Nだってほんとの赤ちゃんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:10.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ！ ひゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:14.35,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（教師ロボット）こらククくん\Nテーブルに乗ってはいけません！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:17.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）ほらクク！\Nコナの邪魔になるからあっち行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ… おっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:25.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,君 コナの絵にケチつけるなら\N欲しがるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:27.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）ほめてたんだよー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それに僕見たもん　本物の赤ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.11,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,えっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,本物の赤ちゃんには 顔がないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:37.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:39.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,トキオも見に行く？
